Dialogue: 0,0:00:00.00,0:00:04.93,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,本作品是設想在首都東京地區發生巨大地震災害
Dialogue: 0,0:00:00.00,0:00:04.93,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,在充分調查與查證的基礎上所製作的虛構故事
Dialogue: 0,0:00:04.96,0:00:10.02,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,原作力求體現真實性 通過模擬實驗而著成
Dialogue: 0,0:00:04.96,0:00:10.02,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,但也存在與現實事物描寫方式不同的地方
Dialogue: 0,0:02:13.01,0:02:16.41,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,未來 只有你一個人真的沒問題嗎
Dialogue: 0,0:02:18.40,0:02:21.16,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,馬上就可以到家了
Dialogue: 0,0:02:21.87,0:02:24.59,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,在學校等等不是更好嗎
Dialogue: 0,0:02:25.59,0:02:27.25,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我想試著找一下家人
Dialogue: 0,0:02:36.48,0:02:37.72,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,回不去了
Dialogue: 0,0:02:38.59,0:02:40.25,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,只有我一個人
Dialogue: 0,0:02:42.20,0:02:43.74,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,沒有悠貴的話
Dialogue: 0,0:02:44.20,0:02:46.50,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,爸爸媽媽會傷心的
Dialogue: 0,0:02:53.58,0:02:57.27,Title,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\fad(460,0)}「給 悠 貴」
Dialogue: 0,0:03:09.09,0:03:10.64,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,為什麼悠貴會
Dialogue: 0,0:03:12.75,0:03:15.78,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,其實 我
Dialogue: 0,0:03:17.46,0:03:19.33,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,已經死了
Dialogue: 0,0:03:23.01,0:03:23.98,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,悠貴
Dialogue: 0,0:03:38.90,0:03:39.84,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,悠貴
Dialogue: 0,0:03:42.09,0:03:43.28,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,回去吧
Dialogue: 0,0:03:58.03,0:03:59.90,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,那個 悠貴
Dialogue: 0,0:04:03.62,0:04:07.56,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,悠貴 已經不在了吧
Dialogue: 0,0:04:09.78,0:04:13.22,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,但是 悠貴太溫柔了
Dialogue: 0,0:04:13.63,0:04:17.71,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,為了不讓姐姐傷心 一直都陪在我身邊呢
Dialogue: 0,0:04:25.53,0:04:28.80,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,因為我想和姐姐在一起
Dialogue: 0,0:04:29.40,0:04:32.38,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,然後一起回家
Dialogue: 0,0:04:32.84,0:04:33.91,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,悠貴
Dialogue: 0,0:04:38.94,0:04:40.04,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,回去吧
Dialogue: 0,0:04:50.75,0:04:54.72,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我一定會把你帶回家的
Dialogue: 0,0:05:08.34,0:05:10.65,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,看 悠貴 到家了
Dialogue: 0,0:05:17.32,0:05:19.33,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,媽媽 也許在家
Dialogue: 0,0:05:24.33,0:05:25.46,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,媽媽
Dialogue: 0,0:05:38.84,0:05:40.40,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,媽媽 媽媽
Dialogue: 0,0:05:49.19,0:05:50.45,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,媽媽
Dialogue: 0,0:05:51.35,0:05:52.32,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,媽媽
Dialogue: 0,0:06:02.66,0:06:03.97,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,姐姐
Dialogue: 0,0:06:08.91,0:06:10.38,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,謝謝你
Dialogue: 0,0:06:13.15,0:06:14.27,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,悠貴
Dialogue: 0,0:06:22.33,0:06:26.10,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,不要 悠貴 不要消失
Dialogue: 0,0:06:29.75,0:06:30.77,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,什麼
Dialogue: 0,0:06:30.93,0:06:32.40,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,你在說什麼
Dialogue: 0,0:06:37.37,0:06:39.96,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,什麼 我聽不到
Dialogue: 0,0:06:40.35,0:06:43.37,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我聽不到啊 悠貴
Dialogue: 0,0:06:45.94,0:06:47.36,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,不要走
Dialogue: 0,0:06:49.81,0:06:52.65,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,姐姐 我最喜歡你了
Dialogue: 0,0:06:58.97,0:07:00.30,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,未來
Dialogue: 0,0:07:01.17,0:07:02.06,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,媽媽
Dialogue: 0,0:07:04.76,0:07:06.25,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,未來
Dialogue: 0,0:07:07.20,0:07:08.23,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,媽媽
Dialogue: 0,0:07:16.75,0:07:17.88,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,媽媽
Dialogue: 0,0:07:36.20,0:07:38.01,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,悠貴
Dialogue: 0,0:07:47.88,0:07:49.80,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,姐姐很了不起啊
Dialogue: 0,0:07:50.34,0:07:51.62,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,那麼辛苦
Dialogue: 0,0:07:56.32,0:07:59.12,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,太好了 活著回來了
Dialogue: 0,0:07:59.23,0:08:00.80,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,但是 悠貴他
Dialogue: 0,0:08:02.39,0:08:04.82,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,對不起 我
Dialogue: 0,0:08:04.93,0:08:08.60,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,不是未來的錯 是媽媽不對
Dialogue: 0,0:08:08.89,0:08:11.27,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,單獨讓你們兩個人出去
Dialogue: 0,0:08:11.74,0:08:16.69,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,不是的 因為我和你們吵了架
Dialogue: 0,0:08:17.01,0:08:19.23,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,所以 悠貴他
Dialogue: 0,0:08:20.96,0:08:21.93,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,未來
Dialogue: 0,0:08:27.17,0:08:28.44,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,很感謝呢
Dialogue: 0,0:08:28.65,0:08:31.21,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,到最後都在悠貴身邊
Dialogue: 0,0:08:33.07,0:08:36.11,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,是悠貴一直都在我身邊
Dialogue: 0,0:08:36.73,0:08:38.92,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,一直都陪著我到家
Dialogue: 0,0:08:40.84,0:08:43.01,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,為了不讓我傷心
Dialogue: 0,0:08:43.43,0:08:45.21,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,為了不讓我停止腳步
Dialogue: 0,0:08:45.26,0:08:47.33,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,為了讓我回到家
Dialogue: 0,0:08:47.74,0:08:50.50,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,一直都在我身邊
Dialogue: 0,0:08:51.79,0:08:55.86,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,所以我能回來都是因為悠貴
Dialogue: 0,0:08:57.52,0:08:59.54,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,悠貴一直都在說
Dialogue: 0,0:09:00.25,0:09:04.43,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,回家了要和爸爸媽媽說好多話
Dialogue: 0,0:09:04.58,0:09:08.74,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,還要和大家一起去台場 還有爺爺家
Dialogue: 0,0:09:09.39,0:09:12.74,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,那孩子 想要和大家一起出去
Dialogue: 0,0:09:13.17,0:09:17.48,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,想要一家人手牽手一起走過大橋
Dialogue: 0,0:09:17.90,0:09:22.28,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,悠貴也不知道說了多少遍 回家吧
Dialogue: 0,0:09:25.54,0:09:26.87,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,未來
Dialogue: 0,0:09:27.58,0:09:28.45,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,未來
Dialogue: 0,0:09:29.14,0:09:30.28,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,悠貴
Dialogue: 0,0:09:31.16,0:09:32.61,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,悠貴
Dialogue: 0,0:09:35.59,0:09:37.14,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,悠貴
Dialogue: 0,0:10:09.33,0:10:10.36,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,未來呢
Dialogue: 0,0:10:11.92,0:10:14.26,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,好像還沒起來
Dialogue: 0,0:10:15.77,0:10:16.89,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,那樣啊
Dialogue: 0,0:10:31.67,0:10:32.87,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,悠貴
Dialogue: 0,0:10:48.61,0:10:51.12,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,姐姐 我畫了個青蛙
Dialogue: 0,0:11:25.52,0:11:28.62,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,這個 還是不要做了比較好吧
Dialogue: 0,0:11:38.72,0:11:41.81,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,早飯做好了 一起來吃吧
Dialogue: 0,0:11:46.29,0:11:49.10,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\an8}東京灣北部地震發生一個月以來
Dialogue: 0,0:11:49.25,0:11:52.55,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\an8}現在已經逐漸恢復寧靜
Dialogue: 0,0:11:52.80,0:11:56.60,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\an8}但是現在還有很多區域還沒恢復生命線的供給
Dialogue: 0,0:11:56.78,0:11:58.82,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\an8}各地制定的對策
Dialogue: 0,0:12:17.28,0:12:21.29,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,忙忙碌碌的 8月馬上都要結束了呢
Dialogue: 0,0:12:23.28,0:12:24.49,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,這樣啊
Dialogue: 0,0:12:28.32,0:12:30.42,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,是 來了
Dialogue: 0,0:12:38.92,0:12:41.69,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,你好 我是日下部
Dialogue: 0,0:12:42.69,0:12:44.90,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,是真理小姐吧
Dialogue: 0,0:12:45.38,0:12:46.40,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,是的
Dialogue: 0,0:12:46.75,0:12:47.88,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,不好意思
Dialogue: 0,0:12:48.09,0:12:51.33,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,本來應該早點來拜訪的
Dialogue: 0,0:12:51.51,0:12:53.32,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,哪裡的話 我們才是
Dialogue: 0,0:12:53.57,0:12:55.69,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,要麻煩你過來一趟
Dialogue: 0,0:12:56.33,0:12:58.47,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,那孩子一定會高興的
Dialogue: 0,0:12:59.89,0:13:02.31,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,那麼 未來呢
Dialogue: 0,0:13:06.74,0:13:07.84,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,未來
Dialogue: 0,0:13:13.07,0:13:14.24,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,真理姐姐
Dialogue: 0,0:13:15.78,0:13:17.95,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,瘦了點呢
Dialogue: 0,0:13:18.69,0:13:19.89,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,那樣啊
Dialogue: 0,0:13:20.46,0:13:22.81,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,明明有好好吃飯的
Dialogue: 0,0:13:25.73,0:13:27.22,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,好耀眼啊
Dialogue: 0,0:13:27.91,0:13:31.56,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,這樣的話活著的人反倒是更辛苦呢
Dialogue: 0,0:13:31.82,0:13:34.41,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,新的一天 太陽升起來
Dialogue: 0,0:13:34.91,0:13:37.35,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,周圍看著都那麼美好
Dialogue: 0,0:13:37.91,0:13:40.16,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,總覺得會看出神呢
Dialogue: 0,0:13:41.75,0:13:43.28,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我丈夫呢
Dialogue: 0,0:13:43.76,0:13:46.49,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,突然從我眼前消失的時候
Dialogue: 0,0:13:46.76,0:13:48.75,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,就是那樣的感覺
Dialogue: 0,0:13:49.13,0:13:51.77,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,葬禮的事完全都不記得了
Dialogue: 0,0:13:52.27,0:13:55.09,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,那個時候是怎麼活過來的啊
Dialogue: 0,0:13:55.82,0:14:00.53,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,但是 菲娜她啊 每天都在長大
Dialogue: 0,0:14:00.86,0:14:03.84,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,會笑啊 會說話了啊
Dialogue: 0,0:14:04.17,0:14:07.29,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,打噴嚏的時候會有點像我丈夫
Dialogue: 0,0:14:09.06,0:14:12.14,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,未來和悠貴也很像
Dialogue: 0,0:14:13.61,0:14:14.95,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,是嗎
Dialogue: 0,0:14:17.98,0:14:22.00,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,悠貴 一直都在未來的心裡
Dialogue: 0,0:14:23.74,0:14:24.27,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,對了
Dialogue: 0,0:14:26.54,0:14:27.45,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,這個
Dialogue: 0,0:14:40.42,0:14:43.57,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,還有這個
Dialogue: 0,0:14:46.08,0:14:47.80,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,這麼晚才給你 不好意思啊
Dialogue: 0,0:14:49.61,0:14:52.32,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我明明已經扔了的
Dialogue: 0,0:14:54.14,0:14:57.75,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,悠貴他又撿回來帶在身邊了
Dialogue: 0,0:15:10.78,0:15:12.70,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\an7\fs55}媽媽手機\N\N機器人展怎麼樣啊\N\N對不起啊沒能一起去\N\N我會做好晚飯等你們回來\N\N不要吵架早點回來喲
Dialogue: 0,0:15:12.75,0:15:15.24,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,媽媽
Dialogue: 0,0:15:20.04,0:15:21.95,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\an7\fs55}由佳\N\N沒事吧\N\N東京 震的好厲害啊\N\N現在我在靜岡奶奶家\N\N很擔心你 等你聯絡
Dialogue: 0,0:15:21.80,0:15:24.50,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,由佳
Dialogue: 0,0:15:26.60,0:15:28.91,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,沒事呢 由佳
Dialogue: 0,0:15:31.91,0:15:34.61,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,奇怪 真理姐姐發的
Dialogue: 0,0:15:38.16,0:15:39.10,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,悠貴
Dialogue: 0,0:15:42.77,0:15:44.06,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,給姐姐
Dialogue: 0,0:15:44.52,0:15:46.43,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我把手機撿回來了哦
Dialogue: 0,0:15:46.64,0:15:48.80,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,姐姐是手機星人
Dialogue: 0,0:15:48.95,0:15:51.06,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,沒有手機會寂寞的
Dialogue: 0,0:15:52.01,0:15:54.51,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我也想有個手機啊
Dialogue: 0,0:15:54.75,0:15:57.97,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,那樣就可以和姐姐發好多郵件了
Dialogue: 0,0:15:58.08,0:16:02.21,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,那樣的話不能說話的時候也可以很開心呢
Dialogue: 0,0:16:02.46,0:16:04.62,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,還有就是也想拍照
Dialogue: 0,0:16:04.93,0:16:10.02,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,早點回家給媽媽禮物然後再一起拍照吧
Dialogue: 0,0:16:12.19,0:16:15.15,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,所以 我們努力回家吧
Dialogue: 0,0:16:15.49,0:16:16.66,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,悠貴
Dialogue: 0,0:16:17.72,0:16:18.65,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,悠貴
Dialogue: 0,0:16:21.29,0:16:22.57,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,未來
Dialogue: 0,0:16:25.09,0:16:28.42,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,悠貴很努力的做了呢
Dialogue: 0,0:16:28.94,0:16:31.79,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,明明頭就很痛的
Dialogue: 0,0:16:34.02,0:16:36.26,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,明明身體就不舒服
Dialogue: 0,0:16:36.89,0:16:39.02,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,卻沒有抱怨一句
Dialogue: 0,0:16:40.85,0:16:45.35,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,平時明明有很多東西都不喜歡吃的
Dialogue: 0,0:16:45.95,0:16:48.05,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,很硬的麵包之類的都好好的吃下去了
Dialogue: 0,0:16:48.55,0:16:50.30,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,很了不起啊
Dialogue: 0,0:16:52.64,0:16:55.68,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,他真的真的很努力了
Dialogue: 0,0:16:58.17,0:17:00.05,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我該怎麼做啊
Dialogue: 0,0:17:00.56,0:17:02.73,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,悠貴已經不在了
Dialogue: 0,0:17:03.94,0:17:06.43,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,好想再見他啊 見悠貴
Dialogue: 0,0:17:13.65,0:17:15.38,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,把未來叫過來吧
Dialogue: 0,0:17:16.41,0:17:18.22,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,和真理小姐分別的時候
Dialogue: 0,0:17:18.39,0:17:21.49,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,還笑著約定要和她再見面呢
Dialogue: 0,0:17:23.60,0:17:25.69,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,她也需要時間吧
Dialogue: 0,0:17:26.35,0:17:28.58,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,媽媽也不要太勉強了
Dialogue: 0,0:17:29.40,0:17:30.61,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,爸爸也是呢
Dialogue: 0,0:17:32.49,0:17:33.47,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,未來
Dialogue: 0,0:17:36.90,0:17:37.88,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,餓了嗎
Dialogue: 0,0:17:38.15,0:17:39.94,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,還是要喝點什麼
Dialogue: 0,0:17:40.74,0:17:41.63,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,媽媽
Dialogue: 0,0:17:42.14,0:17:44.24,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,雖然晚了很多
Dialogue: 0,0:17:44.48,0:17:46.66,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,生日快樂
Dialogue: 0,0:17:48.24,0:17:50.09,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,是悠貴選的
Dialogue: 0,0:17:50.46,0:17:53.06,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,說媽媽喜歡花的
Dialogue: 0,0:18:00.83,0:18:03.13,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,還有這個也是
Dialogue: 0,0:18:04.59,0:18:06.71,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,悠貴給媽媽的
Dialogue: 0,0:18:11.20,0:18:14.54,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,好高興啊 爸爸你看啊
Dialogue: 0,0:18:15.93,0:18:18.45,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,媽媽和未來畫的好像啊
Dialogue: 0,0:18:18.71,0:18:20.16,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,這個是爸爸啊
Dialogue: 0,0:18:20.62,0:18:23.83,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,這樣啊 爸爸的臉是這樣啊
Dialogue: 0,0:18:25.01,0:18:25.96,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,悠貴
Dialogue: 0,0:18:27.10,0:18:30.83,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,家裡充滿著悠貴的味道
Dialogue: 0,0:18:31.51,0:18:34.09,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,不管是睡著還是醒著還是做著什麼
Dialogue: 0,0:18:34.90,0:18:37.00,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我都會想起悠貴
Dialogue: 0,0:18:38.28,0:18:43.60,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我一定會一直傷心著難受著
Dialogue: 0,0:18:44.49,0:18:45.46,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,所以
Dialogue: 0,0:18:45.74,0:18:49.72,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我傷心難過到受不了的時候
Dialogue: 0,0:18:50.29,0:18:52.36,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,就會來找你說說話
Dialogue: 0,0:18:53.39,0:18:55.88,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,開心的時候高興得時候
Dialogue: 0,0:18:56.02,0:18:57.20,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我也會告訴你的
Dialogue: 0,0:18:58.18,0:19:00.17,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,所有的事都告訴給悠貴聽
Dialogue: 0,0:19:01.61,0:19:04.59,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,悠貴 謝謝你
Dialogue: 0,0:19:05.18,0:19:07.92,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,謝謝你當了我的弟弟
Dialogue: 0,0:20:53.86,0:20:55.67,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我必須一直走下去
Dialogue: 0,0:21:03.54,0:21:05.01,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,因為悠貴在看著
